[br]i generally agree with mercyy, GE is more useful most of the time. however, i have found that i use GE more on the caster mobs like the earthseer so that if it gets dispelled, i can easily cast it again using the quick cast time.

however, when going after the king of his PH, i like PE as the duration is longer and it has a better chance of stickinf for a longer period of time.

i have also found myself simply killing the king's PH where he is, but when the king spawns, i clear the mobs to the left so i can have the king solo if root breaks, it seems the king likes to break root early most of the time so having him solo helps. 

i have come to love this place as it brings in good money. only problem is that its camped alot, grr....
